 “Paul's Boutique”十字路口正式更名为 Beastie Boys Square https://www.nme.com/news/music/pauls-boutique-intersection-officially-renamed-beastie-boys-square-3495757?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=pauls-boutique-intersection-officially-renamed-beastie-男孩广场Will RichardsSun, 10 Sep 2023 12:11:17 +0000 Music NewsNewsRap https://www.nme.com/?p=3495757 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/beastie-boys-square-getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="野兽男孩" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/beastie-boys-square-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/beastie-boys-square-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/beastie-boys-square-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/beastie-boys-square-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/beastie-boys-square-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/beastie-boys-square-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Ad-Rock 和 Mike D 在下东区的宣布仪式上发表讲话</p><p>后<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pauls-boutique-intersection-officially-renamed-beastie-boys-square-3495757">“Paul&#39;s Boutique”十字路口正式更名为 Beastie Boys Square，</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/beastie-boys-square-getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="野兽男孩" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/beastie-boys-square-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/beastie-boys-square-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/beastie-boys-square-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/beastie-boys-square-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/beastie-boys-square-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/beastie-boys-square-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 《Paul&#39;s Boutique》封面上不朽的曼哈顿十字路口已正式更名为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beastie-boys">Beastie Boys</a> Square。</p><p> 1989 年专辑的封面以下东区的勒德洛 (Ludlow) 和里文顿 (Rivington) 交汇处为特色。</p><p>十年前，发起了一项<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/beastie-boys/74483">以乐队名字命名该地区的</a>活动，但遭到纽约<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beastie-boys-2-27-1243111">社区委员会的拒绝</a>。</p><p>去年，人们证实<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beastie-boys-to-be-honoured-with-street-name-in-new-york-3270698">该活动终于成功</a>，Beastie Boys Square 将成为现实。</p><p>周六（9 月 8 日），乐队在现场举行的仪式上获得了表彰，Ad-Rock 和 Mike D 均在活动中发表了讲话。</p><p> “感谢（纽约）教会我们看什么、听什么、穿什么、如何爱、如何生活，”Ad-Rock 对人群说道。 “我真的很高兴知道 50 年后某个孩子在上学的路上会抬头说，‘野兽男孩到底是什么？为什么他们会得到一个正方形？’”</p><p> Mike D 补充道：“如果没有在纽约长大，我们就不可能成为现在的样子。”</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">纽约历史性的一天！<br /> Beastie Boy Square 揭幕！ <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/BeastieBoys?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#BeastieBoys</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/BeastieBoysSquare?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#BeastieBoysSquare</a><br />哇！ <a href="https://t.co/22E09FLw3N">pic.twitter.com/22E09FLw3N</a></p><p> — Gili Getz #SaveMasaferYatta (@giligetz) <a href="https://twitter.com/giligetz/status/1700580338781573438?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 9 月 9 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">现在就在<a href="https://twitter.com/YouTube?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@YouTube</a>上收看纽约<a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/BeastieBoys?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#BeastieBoys</a> Square 揭幕庆典： <a href="https://t.co/UBFCeYZrNV">https://t.co/UBFCeYZrNV</